OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FMinisters at Holyrood and Westminster
OL,7,Fmay not be able to say what the
OL,8,Fimplications will be from the Supreme
OL,9,FCourt's ruling on the definition of a
OL,10,Fwoman, but its effect is already being
OL,11,Ffelt in the real world.
OL,13,FThis week's court order against
OL,14,FScottish Borders Council made it clear
OL,15,Fthat state schools in Scotland must
OL,16,Fprovide single-sex toilets for pupils.
OL,18,FThe case was brought before the
OL,19,FSupreme Court ruling, but the fact its
OL,20,Foutcome was announced in the following
OL,21,Fdays means it is very much linked.
