OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FIt has implications that reach much
OL,7,Ffurther than Earlston Primary School
OL,8,Fand one council. This case, again,
OL,9,Fmade crystal clear that public bodies
OL,10,Fhave obligations under law that
OL,11,Fcontradict the drift of policymaking
OL,12,Fin recent years.
OL,14,FEvery area of public life has been
OL,15,Faffected by guidance that was aimed at
OL,16,Fmaking life easier for trans and non-
OL,17,Fbinary people.
