OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FThe aim - to help a group of people
OL,7,Fwho often feel alienated be more
OL,8,Fcomfortable - might be laudable, but
OL,9,Fat almost every turn its execution was
OL,10,Fcack-handed.
OL,12,FThe controversial Gender Recognition
OL,13,FReform Act ended up being blocked by
OL,14,Fthe previous Conservative UK
OL,15,FGovernment, a decision that was backed
OL,16,Fby the courts.
