OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FUnsurprisingly, the Scottish
OL,7,FGovernment confirmed it will no longer
OL,8,Fbe pursuing this legislation in the
OL,9,Fwake of the Supreme Court ruling
OL,10,Fdespite legal commentators suggesting
OL,11,Fthe judgment will have little effect
OL,12,Fon the Act.
OL,14,FBloody-mindedness and a refusal to
OL,15,Flisten to critics led to the shambles
OL,16,Fof the Isla Bryson case.
