OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FBryson raped two women and
OL,7,Ftransitioned to self-identify as a
OL,8,Fwoman after being charged but before
OL,9,Fconviction and imprisonment in a
OL,10,Ffemale prison.
OL,12,FFollowing a backlash, Bryson was
OL,13,Ftransferred to a male prison.
OL,15,FNow wider Scottish Government guidance
OL,16,Fwill have to change in the wake of the
OL,17,FSupreme Court ruling last week that
OL,18,Fthe definition of a "woman" in the
OL,19,FEquality Act is based on biology.
