OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FA meeting between SNP ministers and
OL,7,Fthe Equalities and Human Rights
OL,8,FCommission has been postponed to allow
OL,9,Ftalks to first take place with senior
OL,10,Ffigures in the UK Labour Government.
OL,11,FSenior figures at Holyrood hope the
OL,12,Ftalks will flesh out what alterations
OL,13,Fnow have to be made, particularly
OL,14,Faround single-sex spaces.
OL,16,FThis will affect every public body in
OL,17,FScotland and will be a major shift in
OL,18,Fhow public policy operates in Scotland.
