OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FIt will be a major challenge to
OL,7,Fministers and officials to ensure they
OL,8,Fuphold women's rights as has been laid
OL,9,Fout to them by the law while ensuring
OL,10,Fthat trans people's lives are not made
OL,11,Fworse.
OL,13,FSo far, despite their intentions, that
OL,14,Fhas been the ultimate result of
OL,15,Fgovernment actions.
