OL,3,CGender court ruling analysis -
OL,4,CEarlston Primary School judgement
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney is keen to
OL,7,Favoid speaking about this issue as
OL,8,Fmuch as possible - even if he was
OL,9,FNicola Sturgeon's deputy while she
OL,10,Fpushed it - but his administration's
OL,11,Fability to respond to these court
OL,12,Frulings will be a clear signal about
OL,13,Fwhether or not he is succeeding in
OL,14,Fadding delivery ability to lofty
OL,15,Frhetoric.
